## Writing Guidelines

### Tone & Style
- Write for humans first, search engines second
- Use a {{ tone|default('professional yet approachable') }} tone
- Break up text with subheadings every 250-350 words
- Use bullet points and numbered lists for readability
- Include data, statistics, and examples where possible

### Formatting
- Use H2 for main sections
- Use H3 for subsections
- Keep paragraphs 2-4 sentences max
- Add a relevant image every 300-500 words
- Include a table or infographic if data-heavy

### Quality Checks
- [ ] Answers the search intent comprehensively
- [ ] Provides unique value vs competitors
- [ ] Includes actionable takeaways
- [ ] No duplicate content
